INUMBER 1140
NAME 901
MISC
WEIGHT 3
VOLUME 4
SUBSTANCE INDESTRUCTABLE
*DESCRIPTION_START
Charlek is a fluffy plump little ball of sleek black fur. His pointed oversized
ears and enormous padded paws make him appear clumsy, though his bright golden
eyes gaze back at you intelligently.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB MASSAGE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO ALL Charlek arches his sturdy little back, his tail waving happily in the air.
ENDIF
IFVERB KISS -1
  ECHO ALL Charlek nuzzles %N with his shiny cold wet nose as he "mews" delightedly.
ENDIF
IFVERB CARESS -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO ALL Charlek leans against %N, wrapping his tail around %h leg, purring contentedly.
ENDIF
IFVERB HUG -1
  ECHO ALL Charlek tries to maintain his dignity but quickly gives up, snuggling into %N's arms.
ENDIF
IFVERB TOUCH -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO ALL As Charlek lowers his head and flattens his ears his fluffy bottom wiggles in anticipation. Emiting a throaty growl he pounces on the piece of paper that %N tossed, quickly bringing it back and dropping it into %N's hand.
ENDIF
IFVERB RUB -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO ALL Charlek peers out from %N's arms staring at an imaginary foe, hissing and growling protectively.
ENDIF
IFVERB TAP -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO ALL Lying down, Charlek wraps himself around %N's feet, blinking his eyes a few times before falling asleep.
ENDIF
IFVERB POKE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO ALL Charlek yawns, his tiny teeth glistening as he stretches and stands, licking %N's hand affectionately.
ENDIF
IFVERB TICKLE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO ALL Rolling over onto his back Charlek waves his furry padded paws in the air as he glances back at %N with a wild glint in his eye.
ENDIF
IFVERB THUMP -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO ALL Growling playfully, Charlek bats back at %N's hand then thrusts his head against it, nibbling gently on %N's fingers.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
  CLEARVERB
  RANDOM dummy1 1 4 0
  IFVAR dummy1 = 1
    ECHO ALL Looking soulfully up at %N, Charlek meows pitifully as he raises up putting his paws on %N's leg, begging to be picked up.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR dummy1 = 2
    ECHO ALL His little furry body wriggling with impatience, Charlek stares at %N pleadingly as he waits to be picked up.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR dummy1 = 3
    ECHO ALL Trying to get %N's attention by prancing around %h feet, Charlek suddenly trips over his own overly large paws tumbling into a furry heap with a surprised meow.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR dummy1 = 4
    ECHO ALL Noticing that he's being ignored, Charlek playfully sinks his sharp little fangs into %N's ankle, quickly lapping over the reddened spot with his rough tongue and looking up mischeviously.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PULL -1
  CLEARVERB
  RANDOM dummy2 1 4 0
  IFVAR dummy2 = 1
    ECHO ALL Charlek crouches down, his little furry body twitching. Leaping suddenly into %N's lap, Charlek gives %N a wet sloppy lick on the face.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR dummy2 = 2
    ECHO ALL %N cups %h hand into a claw-like shape facing outwards and at eye level with Charlek. Staring intently Charlek tenses, and with a loud growl springs forward burrowing his head into %N's palm, growling and gnawing gently on %h fingers.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR dummy2 = 3
    ECHO ALL Charlek stalks around %N possessively emitting a low throaty growl. Startled by a sudden noise, his tail poofs up to three times its size as he quickly dives between %N's legs.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR dummy2 = 4
    ECHO ALL Pouncing on a tiny piece of fluff Charlek notices his flicking tail. Chasing it around and around in circles he finally collapses in a heap, panting as the tip of his little pink tongue curls upwards towards his velvety black nose.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
;
INUMBER 1151
NAME 184
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
WORN_FEET
ARTICLE SOME
SUBSTANCE BRITTLE
