    ECHO PLAYER As you tap the toes of your shoes together, the strains of a lilting waltz can be heard drifting through the room.
    ECHO OTHERS As %N taps %h toes of %h shoes together, the strains of a lilting waltz can be heard drifting through the room.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB THUMP -1
  IFVAR GEN = 0
    CLEARVERB
    IFITEM -1 WORN
      ECHO PLAYER A beautiful woman appears and gracefully dances with you, swirling around the room in your arms.
      ECHO OTHERS When %N clicks %h heels together a beautiful woman appears and gracefully dances with %N, swirling around the room in %h arms.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
  IFVAR GEN = 1
    CLEARVERB
    IFITEM -1 WORN
      ECHO PLAYER A handsome man appears, sweeping you into his arms and skillfully dances you around the room.
      ECHO OTHERS When %N clicks %h heels together a handsome man appears, sweeps %N into his arms and skillfully dances %i around the room.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB POKE -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFITEM -1 WORN
    ECHO PLAYER A jaunty melody floods the room and you begin tap dancing, doing the most amazing performance of "Shuffling off to Fayd" that you have even seen!
    ECHO OTHERS %N snaps %h fingers and a jaunty melody floods the room as %s begins tap dancing, doing the most amazing performance of "Shuffling off to Fayd" that you have ever seen!
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CARESS -1
  IFVAR GEN = 0
    CLEARVERB
    IFITEM -1 WORN
      ECHO PLAYER The rythmic sound of drums pulse through the room, skillfully you spin the flaming swords that appear in your hands as your body sways sensuously to the music until the swords and music disappear.
      ECHO OTHERS %N gestures and the rythmic sound of drums pulse through the room. Skillfully %s spins the flaming swords that appear in %h hands as %h body sways sensuously to the music, halting as the swords and music vanish.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
  IFVAR GEN = 1
    CLEARVERB
    IFITEM -1 WORN
      ECHO PLAYER As the rythmic sound of drums pulse through the room you can't help but sway your body sensuously to the music, enchanting everyone within view.
      ECHO OTHERS %N gestures and the rythmic sound of drums pulse through the room. %N sways %i body sensuously to the music in a hypnotic dance of passion.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
  IFVAR GEN = 0
    CLEARVERB
    IFITEM -1 WORN
      ECHO PLAYER You stand on your tiptoes and suddenly leap through the air, landing perfectly as you twirl gracefully around.
      ECHO OTHERS %N stands on %h tiptoes and suddenly leaps through the air, landing perfeectly as %s twirls gracrfully around.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
  IFVAR GEN = 1
    CLEARVERB
    IFITEM -1 WORN
      ECHO PLAYER You point your toes, standing on their very tips. You begin twirling and prancing across the room like a prima ballerina.
      ECHO OTHERS %N points %i toes, then balances on their very tips. %N begins twirling and spinning across the room like a prima ballerina.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LEAN -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFITEM -1 WORN
    ECHO PLAYER A delicate tinkling of music fills the air as %N begins to twirl around and a swirl of musical notes burst from the ground and encircle %i.
    ECHO OTHERS %N begins to sing a haunting melody, weaving magic and music together as the "Balad of Gala Tari" is interperted through a beautiful dance of splendor.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
