*DESCRIPTION_START EXAM
This brilliant little star shimmers with a silvery light and looks exactly
like the ones that shine on a warm summer's eve in a crystal clear sky.
*DESCRIPTION_END
VARIABLE shantaexit2
IFPREVERB RUB -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR region ! 0
    ECHO PLAYER As you draw you fingertips across the tiny star it shimmers with a silver light which quickly fades away.
    ECHO OTHERS As %N draws %h fingertips across a tiny star it shimmers with a silver light which quickly fades away.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR region = 0
    ECHO PLAYER As you trace your fingers along the tiny star it shimmers brightly as a dazzling beam of light strikes the ground near your feet and a glowing silver gate appears!
    ECHO OTHERS As %N traces %h fingers along the tiny star it shimmers brightly as a dazzling beam of light strikes the ground near %N's feet and a glowing silver gate appears!
    NEWITEM 9 68 ADJ1=658 VAL2=800 OPEN
    EQUAL shantaexit2 Rnum
  ENDIF
ENDIF
