You find yourself floating on a fluffy white cloud, surrounded by twinkling
stars. Crystal trees and boulders shimmer in the soft light, casting rainbow-
colored beams that streak outwards into the dark blue sky. Far below you,
though obscurred by the billowing cloud of moisture, you can see the forests
and mountains surrounding Fayd. A glowing silver gate stands at the far end
of this magical place.
