INUMBER 809
NAME 731
WEIGHT 2
VOLUME 3
INTERIOR 10
CONTAINER ON
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAM
This long slender ferret has soft light brown fur and two bright black eyes
that are filled with curiosity. It appears to be extremely quick and agile,
and occasionally bares its razor sharp teeth. Around its neck is a thin
leather collar studded with tiny blue sapphires with the name "Rikki" on it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB RUB -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Tavi snuggles up against you, burrowing his head against your shoulder.
  ECHO OTHERS Tavi snuggles up against %N, burrowing his head against %N's shoulder.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CARESS -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER As you stroke him, Tavi makes soft little "squeaky" noises as he rubs his head against your hand.
  ECHO OTHERS As %N strokes Tavi the ferret makes soft little "squeaky" noises as he rubs his head against %N's hand.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB KISS -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Tavi puts his little wet nose against yours and gives you an affectionate lick.
  ECHO OTHERS Tavi puts his little wet nose against %N's and gives %i an affectionate lick.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB HUG -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Tavi scrambles up on to your shoulder and wraps himself around your neck, giving you a ferret hug!
  ECHO OTHERS Tavi scrambles up on to %N's shoulder and wraps himself around %N's neck, giving %k a ferret hug!
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TAP -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Tavi rolls over and over in your arms with a happy smile on his face.
  ECHO OTHERS Tavi rolls over and over in %N's arms with a happy smile on his face.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB POKE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Tavi's tail goes rigid as he bares his teeth and growls threateningly at anyone or anything approaching you.
  ECHO OTHERS Tavi's tail goes rigid as he bares his teeth and growls threateningly at anyone or anything approaching %N.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Tavi leaps down, streaking out of sight. Dashing back he climbs your legs into your arms as he drops a cookie.
  ECHO OTHERS Tavi leaps down, streaking out of sight. Dashing back Tavi climbs up %N's legs into %h arms as he drops a cookie.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB NUDGE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Tavi scrambles to the ground and lunges at the creature attacking you.
  ECHO OTHERS Tavi rushes to the ground and approaches the attacker of %N.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LEAN -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Tavi digs around in your pouches looking for food, tossing everything out onto the ground as you watch, horrified!
  ECHO OTHERS Tavi digs around in %N pouches looking for food, tossing everything out onto the ground as %N watches, horrified!
ENDIF
IFPREVERB THUMP -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Tavi digs into your money pouch retrieving a copper. Leaping down he races over to an urchin, drops the coin into his palm then leaps back into your arms.
  ECHO OTHERS Tavi digs into %N's money pouch retrieving a copper. Leaping down he races over to an urchin, dropping the coin into his palm then leaps back into %N's arms.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PULL -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Tavi happily munches on one of Firestar's most valuable scrolls.
  ECHO OTHERS Tavi happily munches on one of Firestar's most valuable scrolls.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TURN -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Tavi chatters in your ear, arguing with you about which spell you should use next.
  ECHO OTHERS Tavi suddenly begins chattering at %N. It seems Tavi is advising %N on which spell to use next and it looks like %N is losing the discussion.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CUDDLE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Tavi sniffs the air inquisitively and then growls at the nearest undead creature.
  ECHO OTHERS Tavi sniffs the air inquisitively and then growls at the nearest undead creature.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LICK -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Tavi darts from your shoulder and scampers to the fountain where he begins playfully splashing anyone close by.
  ECHO OTHERS Tavi darts from %N's shoulder and scampers to the fountain where he begins playfully splashing anyone close by.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LISTEN -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Tavi scrambles up onto your shoulder and presses his wet nose to your ear as he whispers to you.
  ECHO OTHERS Tavi scrambles up onto %N's shoulder and presses his wet nose against %N's ear while chittering quietly to %i.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB MASSAGE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Tavi intently studies your book of spells. After a moment he gestures at a lost kitten, chittering in frustration as his spell fails.
  ECHO OTHERS Tavi intently studies %N's book of spells. After a moment he gestures at a lost kitten, chittering in frustration as his spell fails.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB WAVE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER A small brown ferret climbs up on your shoulder and waves to everyone.
  ECHO OTHERS A small brown ferret climbs up on Firestar's shoulder and waves at you.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PINCH -1
  CLEARVERB
