NUMBER 801
NAME Inside Coffin
DARKNESS
INDOOR_FLOOR
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
Though it is very dark in here, you find yourself in a snug comfortable coffin.
The red silk lining feels cool against your skin and a soft pillow supports
your head. The lid above you glows with a faint purple light and looks more
like a door than the top of a coffin.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 66
ITEM 1 193 ADJ1=25 ADJ2=291
IFPREVERB STAND -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You're in a coffin! How can you stand up?
ENDIF
IFPREVERB SIT -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You're in a coffin! How can you sit up?
ENDIF
IFPREVERB KNEEL -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You're in a coffin! How can you kneel?
ENDIF
IFPREVERB EXIT -1
  CLEARVERB
  DISBAND
  IFCARRY 832 -1
    IFVAR ITEMVAL5 > 0
      MOVE ITEMVAL5
      EQUAL ITEMVAL5 0
      IFVAR MISTFORM = 1
        ECHO OTHERS %N seeps out of the coffin.
        ECHO PLAYER You seep under the lid of the coffin and out.
      ELSE
        ECHO PLAYER You push open the lid and climb back out of your coffin.
        ECHO OTHERS %N pushes open the lid and climbs back out of %h coffin.
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
  POSITION STAND
ENDIF
IFVERB TRANSFORM -1
  IFVAR MISTFORM = 0
    POSITION LAY
  ENDIF
ENDIF
