This little dog is very young, barely out of his puppy stage. He has soft
black fur with white feet, white ears and a white patch around his right
eye. His dark eyes twinkle with curiosity as his fluffy tail constantly
wags back and forth. He has a red bandana tied around his neck.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB KISS -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Petey affectionately licks your face over and over again, leaving wet streaks all over your cheeks.
  ECHO OTHERS Petey affectionately licks %N's face over and over again, leaving wet streaks all over %N's cheeks.
ENDIF
  IFPREVERB HUG -1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER Petey dives into the crook in your arm, snuggling up against you.
    ECHO OTHERS Petey dives into the crook in %N's arm, snuggling up against %i.
  ENDIF
IFPREVERB CARESS -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER As you rub Petey's stomach he wiggles around delightedly as he makes happy little "yipping" noises.
