INUMBER 1280
NAME 77
WEIGHT 1500
VOLUME 5
*DESCRIPTION_START
A stream of water shoots upwards from the mouth of a powerful looking lion
which is posed to attack in the center of this impressive fountain. Rivlets
of moisture stream down his mane and flow over the carcass of a boar at his
feet. The huge carved bowel at the base of the sculpture is filled with
sparkling blue water and tiny golden fish.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB TOUCH -1
  ROUTINE 1
ENDIF
IFVERB GO -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You step into the spray from the fountain and dance around like a water nymph.
  ECHO OTHERS %N steps into the spraying water and sloshes around while waving %h arms.
ENDIF
