INUMBER 714
NAME 395
WEIGHT 2
VOLUME 10
INTERIOR 10
CONTAINER IN
VARIABLE shagrow
VARIABLE shacheck
*DESCRIPTION_START
This little portable greenhouse is filled with glowing blue dirt which you
can barely see through the misty plastic walls. "Tap me first" is etched
into the side of the house.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB2 TAP -1
  CLEARVERB
IFVAR ITEMADJ1 = 805
IFVAR ITEMADJ2 = 587
  ECHO PLAYER The earth levels out and packs down inside the greenhouse.
  ECHO OTHERS %N taps against the side of a small greenhouse.
  ADD shacheck 1
ENDIF
ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB2 PUT -1
  CLEARVERB
IFVAR ARCHNUM = 113
  REMOVEITEM -1
  ADD shagrow 1
IFVAR shagrow = 1
IFVAR shacheck => 1
  ECHO PLAYER The moonstone immediately is absorbed into the soil and a little green sprout appears.
  ECHO OTHERS %N carefully puts a moonstone in the little greenhouse.
ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR shagrow = 2
IFVAR shacheck => 1
  ECHO PLAYER The earth dissolves the moonstone  and the little sprout grows several inches and gets thicker.
  ECHO OTHERS %N puts another moonstone into the greenhouse.
ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR shagrow => 3
IFVAR shagrow <= 25
IFVAR shacheck => 1
  ECHO PLAYER The moonstone flashes brilliantly as it disappears as something falls out of the greenhouse to the ground!
  ECHO OTHERS %N drops another moonstone into the greenhouse.
  NEWITEM 9 1688 ADJ1=1235 VAL1=1400 VAL2=2 VAL3=318 VAL5=11
ENDIF
ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR shagrow => 26
IFVAR shacheck => 1
  ECHO PLAYER The moonstone disappears but nothing happens.
  ECHO OTHERS %N stares at the little greenhouse.
ENDIF
ENDIF
ENDIF
ENDIF
