INUMBER 715
NAME 412
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
ARMOR
WORN_NECK
;
INUMBER 805
NAME 803
WEIGHT 5
VOLUME 3
*DESCRIPTION_START
Fluffy shiny brown fur covers the Eekey from head to toe. Its cute furry round
ears are just a little too big for its slender head. Long dark lashes shade its
big wide emerald green eyes which glitter and sparkle and add to its friendly
appearance. A tiny puff of fur tips its short fuzzy tail as well as each of its
paws.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB TOUCH -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER A shimmer of sparks shoot across the Eekey's fur.
  ECHO OTHERS A shimmer of sparks shoots across the Eekey's fur when %N touches it.
  DAMAGEPLR ELECTRIC 5 You feel a jolt of electricity shoot through your body!
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GET -1
  ECHO PLAYER The little Eekey burps out a cloud of foul smelling green gas.
  ECHO OTHERS The little Eekey burps out a cloud of foul smelling green gas.
  DAMAGEALL BURN 10 Something suddenly burns %N!
ENDIF
IFPREVERB WAVE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The tiny Eekey gasps in surprise as a flash of flames shoot from its eyes!
  ECHO OTHERS The tiny Eekey gasps in surprise as a flash of flames shoot from its eyes as %N waves it around in the air!
  DAMAGEALL BURN 5 A little blast of flame encompasses %N
ENDIF
IFPREVERB RUB -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The Eekey's body reverbates with the force of its pleasureable purring.
  ECHO OTHERS As %N rubs the Eekey behind the ears its whole body shakes with the force of its purring.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB HUG -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The cute little Eekey squeeks delightedly as you hug it!
  ECHO OTHERS The cute little Eekey squeeks delightedly as %N hugs it!
ENDIF
IFPREVERB KISS -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You feel a little jolt as the Eekey licks you tenderly back.
  ECHO OTHERS There's a little flash from the Eekey's tongue as it tenderly licks %N.
  DAMAGEPLR ELECTRIC 5 You feel a little zap of electricity!
ENDIF
