INUMBER 1731
NAME 884
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
*DESCRIPTION_START
The cube sparkles and glows with a faint blue light. Its sides and bottom
are too opaque to see through but the top is made of very clear crystal
which permits the viewing of a small triangular shaped emerald floating
magically within the black crystal square.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB TURN -1
  CLEARVERB
  RANDOM dummy1 1 3 0
  IFVAR dummy1 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER The emerald moves to the top of the cube and the word "Yes" inscribed onto the gem can be seen.
    ECHO OTHERS %N turns %h cube over in %h hands a few times and then stares at it.
  ENDIf
  IFVAR dummy1 = 2
    ECHO PLAYER The emerald spins around inside the cube before remaining still and showing a "No" pressing against the top.
    ECHO OTHERS %N turns %h cube over in %h hands a few times and then frowns as %s studies it.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR dummy1 = 3
    ECHO PLAYER Tumbling inside the cube the word "Maybe" finally appears on the surface of the emerald.
    ECHO OTHERS %N turns %h cube over in %h hands a few times, glances at it and then shrugs.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
