multiplied a thousand times over in the solid crystal walls and floor.
The source of the shimmering lights seems to be an enormous tree, whose
gem-like branches cover the ceiling with a mass of emerald leave and rustle
with a soft tinkling sound as it seems to bow in greeting. A wide archway
leads east.
