OUTDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
The road begins to slop up a green hill, from the top of which you can
overlook the fringes of a grand estate. Intricate topiary of verdant serpents.
heroes, and beasts grace the landscape. A lilac edged path winds off to the
east.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 270
EXIT SW 272
ITEM 0 80 VAL2=842
;
INUMBER 1405
NAME 885
WEIGHT 1500
VOLUME 50
INTERIOR 50
CONTAINER ON
PORTAL
;
INUMBER 1406
NAME 888
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
WORN_DON
IFVERB WEAR -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You wrap the shawl around your shoulders.
  ECHO OTHERS %N wraps a shawl around %h shoulders.
ENDIF
