INUMBER 1820
NAME 1458
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 20
INTERIOR 20
CONTAINER IN
*DESCRIPTION_START
The tiny bird is covered with a soft blue fuzz, its little wings very slender
and not yet fully developed. Its small dark eyes are filled with trust and
its yellow beak just large enough to gulp down a worm.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB KISS -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The baby bird gently touches its beak to your lips.
  ECHO OTHERS A baby bird gently touches its beak to %N's lips.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB HUG -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The tiny bird flutters its wings contentedly as it snuggles up against you.
  ECHO OTHERS A tiny baby bird flutters its wings contentedly as it snuggles up against %i.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TOUCH -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The baby bird hops onto your shoulder and pecks playfully at your ear.
  ECHO OTHERS A baby bird hops onto %N's shoulder and pecks playfully at %h ear.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The little bird flaps its wings energetically but doesn't manage to fly.
  ECHO OTHERS A little baby bird perched on %N's shoulder flaps its wings energetically but doesn't manage to fly.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TAP -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The tiny baby bird opens its beak and squawks hungrily at you.
  ECHO OTHERS A tiny baby bird opens its beak and squawks hungrily at %N.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CARESS -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER As you gently stroke the baby bird it chirps happily and relaxes against you.
  ECHO OTHERS As %N gently strokes a baby bird it chirps happily and relaxes against %i.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUT -1
IFVAR ARCHNUM ! 1469
  ECHO PLAYER The baby bird snaps its beak shut, turns its head away looking very upset and hungry.
  ECHO OTHERS A baby bird snaps its beak shut and turns away from %N and what %s is trying to feed it.
ENDIF
IFVAR ARCHNUM = 1469
  REMOVEITEM -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You dangle the worm infront of the baby bird. It snaps it up in its beak and gulps it down!
  ECHO OTHERS %N dangles a worm infront of a baby bird. It snaps up the worm in its beak and gulps it down!
ENDIF
ENDIF
;
