INUMBER 1290
NAME 668
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 2
CONTAINER IN
OPENABLE
*DESCRIPTION_START
This durable bedroll is made of the finest weather-proofed cotton available
and has a very sturdy metal zipper.
*DESCRIPTION_END
VARIABLE shantexit5
IFITEM -1 OPEN
  EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
IFVERB GO -1
  CLEARVERB
  DISBAND
  ECHO PLAYER You unzip the bedroll, crawl inside and snuggle down then zip it up.
  ECHO OTHERS %N unzips %h bedroll and crawls inside, zipping it up.
  CLOSE -1
  MOVE 3814
  EQUAL shantexit5 RNUM
ENDIF
ENDIF
;
NUMBER 3814
NAME Inside Bedroll
DARKNESS
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
You can feel the soft fleece lining brushing against your skin and a pleasant
warmth spreading throughout your body. Wild fowl, in various positions of
flight, have been embroidered on the soft blue interior.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 72
IFPREVERB GO 0
  CLEARVERB
  DISBAND
  ECHO PLAYER You unzips the bedroll and crawls out.
  ECHO OTHERS %N unzips the bedroll and crawls out.
  MOVE shantexit5
ENDIF
;
